WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:19.686 --> 00:00:20.895 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS gasping]

00:00:20.979 --> 00:00:22.522 position:50% align:center
The waves are ferocious!

00:00:22.605 --> 00:00:26.443 position:50% align:center
Put your backs into those
oars and keep us on track!

00:00:26.526 --> 00:00:29.195 position:50% align:center
The wind is also quite fierce.

00:00:29.279 --> 00:00:30.655 position:50% align:center
We have 3,000!

00:00:30.739 --> 00:00:32.157 position:50% align:center
They have 1,000!

00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:34.242 position:50% align:center
We Genji have fortune
on our side!

00:00:34.325 --> 00:00:37.245 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS cheer]

00:00:37.328 --> 00:00:38.705 position:50% align:center
They may have the numbers,

00:00:38.788 --> 00:00:41.207 position:50% align:center
but we Heike excel
in combat at sea!

00:00:41.291 --> 00:00:42.375 position:50% align:center
Show them what we can do!

00:00:42.459 --> 00:00:45.128 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS cheer]

00:00:55.180 --> 00:00:56.514 position:50% align:center
[YOSHITSUNE growls]

00:01:00.101 --> 00:01:01.186 position:50% align:center
Fire!

00:01:01.269 --> 00:01:02.854 position:50% align:center
Fire!

00:02:36.781 --> 00:02:39.701 position:50% align:center
[chirping]

00:02:39.784 --> 00:02:42.245 position:50% align:center
Ah, a shrike?

00:02:42.328 --> 00:02:44.664 position:50% align:center
It's a deceptively
adorable bird.

00:02:44.748 --> 00:02:47.167 position:50% align:center
One that impales its
prey on sharp branches.

00:02:47.250 --> 00:02:48.460 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:02:48.543 --> 00:02:50.337 position:50% align:center
I imagine right now,

00:02:50.420 --> 00:02:52.505 position:50% align:center
Yoshitsune is leading
the Genji warriors

00:02:52.589 --> 00:02:55.091 position:50% align:center
to inflict the same
fate upon the Heike.

00:02:55.175 --> 00:02:56.801 position:50% align:center
Ah...

00:02:59.429 --> 00:03:03.099 position:50% align:center
[GO-SHIRAKAWA]
The skies are remarkably clear!

00:03:03.183 --> 00:03:05.018 position:50% align:center
Must be some kind of omen.

00:03:05.101 --> 00:03:10.148 position:50% align:center
Perhaps the Sacred Treasures
will soon return to the capital.

00:03:11.149 --> 00:03:19.282 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS gasping]

00:03:19.366 --> 00:03:20.492 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI]
Board their boat!

00:03:20.575 --> 00:03:22.452 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS shouting]

00:03:22.535 --> 00:03:25.330 position:50% align:center
Let us follow Lord
Tomomori's lead!

00:03:25.413 --> 00:03:26.623 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS shouting]

00:03:26.706 --> 00:03:29.584 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS yelling]

00:03:29.668 --> 00:03:31.961 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI grunting]

00:03:32.045 --> 00:03:34.172 position:50% align:center
Push hard when I say!

00:03:34.255 --> 00:03:35.298 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER A]
No!

00:03:35.382 --> 00:03:36.299 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER B]
I'm gonna fall!

00:03:36.383 --> 00:03:39.594 position:50% align:center
Ready, push!

00:03:39.678 --> 00:03:41.721 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS chattering]

00:03:41.805 --> 00:03:43.807 position:50% align:center
[screaming]

00:03:47.185 --> 00:03:49.145 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER C gasps]

00:03:52.357 --> 00:03:56.695 position:50% align:center
Don't falter, men!
And row like mad!

00:03:56.778 --> 00:03:59.239 position:50% align:center
Force them into the whirlpool!

00:03:59.322 --> 00:04:02.701 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS screaming]

00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:06.955 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS cheer]

00:04:08.873 --> 00:04:12.627 position:50% align:center
Hmph. We've turned the tide
on those damned Genji!

00:04:12.711 --> 00:04:14.921 position:50% align:center
Attack! Attack!

00:04:15.005 --> 00:04:15.880 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS yell]

00:04:15.964 --> 00:04:17.215 position:50% align:center
[SOLDIERS shouting]

00:04:17.298 --> 00:04:20.510 position:50% align:center
Uh... How do things look?

00:04:20.593 --> 00:04:22.554 position:50% align:center
It seems that we
have the advantage.

00:04:22.637 --> 00:04:27.559 position:50% align:center
Good! Now hand me a bow!

00:04:27.642 --> 00:04:28.893 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:04:36.026 --> 00:04:37.277 position:50% align:center
Mother, please.

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:39.487 position:50% align:center
I would very much like
to see the battle myself.

00:04:39.571 --> 00:04:40.864 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO]
It's too dangerous.

00:04:40.947 --> 00:04:43.450 position:50% align:center
But Mother,
I am still the Emperor!

00:04:43.533 --> 00:04:44.743 position:50% align:center
♪

00:04:46.286 --> 00:04:49.080 position:50% align:center
[BIWA] I imagine you can see it
if you promise you won't cry

00:04:49.164 --> 00:04:51.124 position:50% align:center
if an arrow strikes you.

00:04:52.459 --> 00:04:54.794 position:50% align:center
That kind of pain is no fun.

00:04:57.464 --> 00:05:03.428 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS yelling]

00:05:03.511 --> 00:05:06.806 position:50% align:center
That's the way! Keep going
till we crush the Genji!

00:05:06.890 --> 00:05:08.224 position:50% align:center
Push with me!

00:05:08.308 --> 00:05:12.812 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS yelling]

00:05:14.606 --> 00:05:16.858 position:50% align:center
Lord Yoshitsune, between
this and the current,

00:05:16.941 --> 00:05:18.735 position:50% align:center
our boats can't advance!

00:05:18.818 --> 00:05:22.364 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER E]
Retreat may be our best option!

00:05:22.447 --> 00:05:24.991 position:50% align:center
We still have them
greatly outnumbered.

00:05:25.075 --> 00:05:29.704 position:50% align:center
The Heike forces will
surely tire before long.

00:05:29.788 --> 00:05:32.499 position:50% align:center
Ride it out, My Lord!

00:05:39.089 --> 00:05:41.508 position:50% align:center
[gasps] Something's changed.

00:05:41.591 --> 00:05:42.759 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:05:48.431 --> 00:05:52.394 position:50% align:center
[MUNEMORI gasping]
What now?

00:05:58.066 --> 00:05:59.984 position:50% align:center
Seriously?

00:06:03.905 --> 00:06:05.407 position:50% align:center
[YOSHITSUNE]
Dolphins?

00:06:07.659 --> 00:06:09.035 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIER A]
Lord Munemori!

00:06:09.119 --> 00:06:12.455 position:50% align:center
Well, according to
what the onmyoji says,

00:06:12.539 --> 00:06:14.666 position:50% align:center
if those dolphins swim
to the Genji side,

00:06:14.749 --> 00:06:16.126 position:50% align:center
the Genji shall fall.

00:06:16.209 --> 00:06:20.046 position:50% align:center
But if they continue over
to our side, then...

00:06:24.426 --> 00:06:27.220 position:50% align:center
This makes me feel so nostalgic.

00:06:34.644 --> 00:06:36.604 position:50% align:center
[YOSHITSUNE]
Our banners...

00:06:36.688 --> 00:06:38.857 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI]
The winds have shifted.

00:06:40.775 --> 00:06:46.448 position:50% align:center
[MUNEMORI] Stay back! Go away!
Don't come near us!

00:06:55.290 --> 00:06:57.876 position:50% align:center
It suits you.
I love this hairstyle.

00:06:57.959 --> 00:06:59.502 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:07:01.838 --> 00:07:05.383 position:50% align:center
[MUNEMORI whimpering]

00:07:05.467 --> 00:07:07.552 position:50% align:center
[YOSHITSUNE]
Even the wind is on our side!

00:07:07.635 --> 00:07:09.721 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIERS cheer]

00:07:09.804 --> 00:07:12.182 position:50% align:center
I want you to shoot
at their oarsmen!

00:07:12.265 --> 00:07:14.809 position:50% align:center
Shoot their oarsmen, now!

00:07:14.893 --> 00:07:17.437 position:50% align:center
Shoot the enemy
oarsmen, now!

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:19.606 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER H gasping]

00:07:19.689 --> 00:07:20.482 position:50% align:center
[yelps]

00:07:20.565 --> 00:07:21.441 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI gasps]

00:07:21.524 --> 00:07:23.401 position:50% align:center
[grunting]

00:07:23.485 --> 00:07:27.822 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIER C]
We're being swept away!

00:07:27.906 --> 00:07:29.157 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER I]
The current has shifted!

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:31.785 position:50% align:center
We can capsize them!

00:07:41.086 --> 00:07:43.004 position:50% align:center
Lord Tomomori!

00:07:44.964 --> 00:07:47.634 position:50% align:center
Lord Yoshitsune!
There are boats approaching!

00:07:47.717 --> 00:07:49.636 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER J]
Lord Yoshitsune!

00:07:49.719 --> 00:07:54.349 position:50% align:center
We're here to lend our
strength to the Genji!

00:07:54.432 --> 00:07:58.520 position:50% align:center
We have the momentum now!
Let's give it all we've got!

00:07:58.603 --> 00:08:01.022 position:50% align:center
[SOLDIERS yelling]

00:08:01.106 --> 00:08:02.774 position:50% align:center
[SUKEMORI growls]

00:08:04.567 --> 00:08:09.864 position:50% align:center
[gasps] This is terrifying!
I need to get to Mother's boat!

00:08:12.450 --> 00:08:16.413 position:50% align:center
[panting]

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:31.136 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIER D]
Lord Munemori!

00:08:31.219 --> 00:08:33.847 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO] Munemori. What's
happening over there?

00:08:33.930 --> 00:08:37.183 position:50% align:center
[MUNEMORI]
Th-The battle's still undecided.

00:08:42.188 --> 00:08:46.067 position:50% align:center
Brother... What becomes of
the emperor if we lose?

00:08:46.151 --> 00:08:48.737 position:50% align:center
The emperor would most likely
be taken to the capital

00:08:48.820 --> 00:08:50.864 position:50% align:center
to conduct a formal abdication.

00:08:50.947 --> 00:08:54.200 position:50% align:center
The title would then
belong to young Go-Toba.

00:08:54.284 --> 00:08:56.661 position:50% align:center
Ah, so his life will be spared.

00:08:56.745 --> 00:08:59.164 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO] That may be true,
but all our efforts,

00:08:59.247 --> 00:09:01.291 position:50% align:center
our indignities, all we've
done to protect him

00:09:01.374 --> 00:09:04.002 position:50% align:center
and the Sacred Treasures
would be rendered meaningless!

00:09:04.085 --> 00:09:05.920 position:50% align:center
What are you saying?

00:09:06.004 --> 00:09:08.506 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO] To hand either
over at this time...

00:09:08.590 --> 00:09:10.258 position:50% align:center
What would be the
point of everything

00:09:10.342 --> 00:09:12.260 position:50% align:center
we've been forced
to suffer through?

00:09:12.344 --> 00:09:14.054 position:50% align:center
We would've sacrificed
for nothing!

00:09:14.137 --> 00:09:18.141 position:50% align:center
The battle has not been
decided yet, Mother!

00:09:18.224 --> 00:09:20.852 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO]
Surviving is a hollow existence.

00:09:20.935 --> 00:09:24.898 position:50% align:center
What awaits is a life far worse
than this one's become.

00:09:28.234 --> 00:09:29.152 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO]
It must be done.

00:09:29.235 --> 00:09:31.613 position:50% align:center
[gasps] Mother, no!

00:09:31.696 --> 00:09:34.157 position:50% align:center
How poorly do you think
the emperor will be treated

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:37.994 position:50% align:center
once they have robbed
him of his position?

00:09:38.078 --> 00:09:41.206 position:50% align:center
And what of you? After they
capture you, I'd expect you

00:09:41.289 --> 00:09:44.501 position:50% align:center
to be forcibly married
to some worthless Genji.

00:09:44.584 --> 00:09:48.797 position:50% align:center
Do you still claim you
can protect the emperor?

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:50.215 position:50% align:center
[BENKEI]
Lord Yoshitsune,

00:09:50.298 --> 00:09:52.801 position:50% align:center
the emperor is not
on a Chinese ship.

00:09:52.884 --> 00:09:55.261 position:50% align:center
We were able to get that much
information from a soldier

00:09:55.345 --> 00:09:57.639 position:50% align:center
who's switched sides
from the Heike.

00:09:57.722 --> 00:10:00.183 position:50% align:center
Is that so? Listen well!

00:10:00.266 --> 00:10:04.521 position:50% align:center
The emperor's on a small boat!
Attack all of those you can see!

00:10:04.604 --> 00:10:06.940 position:50% align:center
[gasping]

00:10:07.023 --> 00:10:08.441 position:50% align:center
You hear that?

00:10:08.525 --> 00:10:11.778 position:50% align:center
Lord Tomomori, they know the
emperor is on a small boat!

00:10:11.861 --> 00:10:14.364 position:50% align:center
Death to those
who've betrayed us!

00:10:14.447 --> 00:10:16.116 position:50% align:center
Lord Tomomori...

00:10:16.199 --> 00:10:17.575 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS screaming]

00:10:21.579 --> 00:10:24.541 position:50% align:center
There's no coming
back from this.

00:10:24.624 --> 00:10:27.460 position:50% align:center
Head for Tokuko's boat at once!

00:10:29.713 --> 00:10:31.256 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIER G]
Lord Tomomori!

00:10:31.339 --> 00:10:34.676 position:50% align:center
Oh! It's you! I'm so
happy you're safe!

00:10:34.759 --> 00:10:36.511 position:50% align:center
Glad to see you as well.

00:10:36.594 --> 00:10:38.722 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasp]

00:10:38.805 --> 00:10:40.849 position:50% align:center
You're still alive!

00:10:43.226 --> 00:10:45.020 position:50% align:center
What of the battle?

00:10:46.438 --> 00:10:47.731 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI whimpers]

00:10:47.814 --> 00:10:50.650 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:10:50.734 --> 00:10:52.819 position:50% align:center
Huh...?

00:10:52.902 --> 00:10:56.740 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:10:56.823 --> 00:10:59.242 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI] You ladies will
soon be witness to creatures

00:10:59.325 --> 00:11:04.205 position:50% align:center
you've never seen before,
men from the east!

00:11:04.289 --> 00:11:05.915 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI laughing]

00:11:07.917 --> 00:11:10.879 position:50% align:center
What's all this noise?

00:11:10.962 --> 00:11:14.716 position:50% align:center
I refuse be taken by
those Genji brutes.

00:11:14.799 --> 00:11:17.302 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO gasping]

00:11:17.385 --> 00:11:18.636 position:50% align:center
[ANTOKU]
Huh...?

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:20.805 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO] Take my hand and
come with me, Emperor.

00:11:20.889 --> 00:11:22.349 position:50% align:center
[gasping]

00:11:24.642 --> 00:11:28.271 position:50% align:center
[ANTOKU] Where are we going
at a time like this?

00:11:28.355 --> 00:11:30.190 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO]
To a beautiful place.

00:11:30.273 --> 00:11:33.568 position:50% align:center
One that is known as
the Pure Land paradise.

00:11:34.778 --> 00:11:37.238 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO]
Mother...

00:11:37.322 --> 00:11:39.866 position:50% align:center
[TOKIKO]
Bring forth the Treasures.

00:11:39.949 --> 00:11:44.245 position:50% align:center
Just a moment, Mother. I can
buy you a little more time.

00:12:02.681 --> 00:12:03.473 position:50% align:center
[SOLDIERS grunting]

00:12:03.556 --> 00:12:04.724 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER L yelling]

00:12:04.808 --> 00:12:07.352 position:50% align:center
[GENJI SOLDIER M] There it is!
That's the boat!

00:14:04.844 --> 00:14:10.058 position:50% align:center
[gasps] Tokuko! Tokuko!

00:14:15.146 --> 00:14:16.356 position:50% align:center
[BIWA]
Tokuko!

00:14:16.439 --> 00:14:18.024 position:50% align:center
[splash]

00:14:29.911 --> 00:14:33.498 position:50% align:center
Not yet. Your story isn't over.

00:14:33.581 --> 00:14:35.583 position:50% align:center
[COURT LADY A]
The Empress Dowager!

00:14:35.667 --> 00:14:36.626 position:50% align:center
What happened?

00:14:36.710 --> 00:14:38.420 position:50% align:center
His Majesty's mother
just fell in!

00:14:38.503 --> 00:14:40.422 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIER J]
Hurry! Pull her up!

00:14:45.552 --> 00:14:47.262 position:50% align:center
I have Her Majesty!

00:14:47.345 --> 00:14:49.431 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO]
No!

00:14:49.514 --> 00:14:54.728 position:50% align:center
Stay away! Don't touch me!

00:14:54.811 --> 00:14:59.024 position:50% align:center
No! Listen. It's not time!

00:14:59.107 --> 00:15:01.693 position:50% align:center
Your life needs to go on!
You have to live!

00:15:01.776 --> 00:15:05.113 position:50% align:center
Please... Let me go with them!

00:15:05.196 --> 00:15:07.824 position:50% align:center
With this eye,
I see the future!

00:15:07.907 --> 00:15:10.452 position:50% align:center
And you live on--
for everyone's sake,

00:15:10.535 --> 00:15:12.662 position:50% align:center
because they can't!

00:15:12.746 --> 00:15:16.082 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO coughing]

00:15:17.459 --> 00:15:21.212 position:50% align:center
And this eye... This is
the one I got from Shigemori!

00:15:21.296 --> 00:15:25.300 position:50% align:center
I see them, Tokuko. All of them.

00:15:25.383 --> 00:15:26.760 position:50% align:center
I see the emperor--

00:15:26.843 --> 00:15:30.972 position:50% align:center
his tiny hands are pressed
together in prayer.

00:15:33.058 --> 00:15:37.520 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO wailing]

00:15:39.314 --> 00:15:41.941 position:50% align:center
The emperor?

00:15:42.025 --> 00:15:44.277 position:50% align:center
He's gone.

00:15:44.361 --> 00:15:45.653 position:50% align:center
I understand.

00:15:45.737 --> 00:15:47.030 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIER N yells]

00:15:47.113 --> 00:15:50.658 position:50% align:center
[HEIKE SOLDIERS yelling]

00:15:50.742 --> 00:15:53.161 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI exhales]

00:15:53.244 --> 00:15:57.582 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI] That's it. I've
seen all that I need to see.

00:16:03.755 --> 00:16:05.465 position:50% align:center
What's this?

00:16:08.259 --> 00:16:11.179 position:50% align:center
[TOMOMORI] All of you who still
hold the Heike name dear!

00:16:11.262 --> 00:16:13.390 position:50% align:center
Follow me this one last time!

00:16:13.473 --> 00:16:17.185 position:50% align:center
[yelling]

00:16:28.863 --> 00:16:30.865 position:50% align:center
Namu Amida Bu.

00:16:38.623 --> 00:16:41.459 position:50% align:center
[MUNEMORI cries]

00:16:45.714 --> 00:16:46.965 position:50% align:center
[COURT LADY A wails]

00:16:47.048 --> 00:16:49.009 position:50% align:center
[MUNEMORI grunts]

00:17:42.812 --> 00:17:45.815 position:50% align:center
[exhales, laughs]

00:17:45.899 --> 00:17:47.108 position:50% align:center
Hm?

00:17:52.489 --> 00:17:54.699 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO gasping]

00:17:57.410 --> 00:17:59.829 position:50% align:center
[GO-SHIRAKAWA] You were once
the wife of an emperor.

00:17:59.913 --> 00:18:02.290 position:50% align:center
For you to live in such
a meager dwelling...

00:18:02.374 --> 00:18:06.294 position:50% align:center
Do you not feel disgraced
or constricted by it all?

00:18:06.378 --> 00:18:10.006 position:50% align:center
Honestly, I did feel that
way at a certain point.

00:18:10.090 --> 00:18:12.509 position:50% align:center
However, this is a welcome stop

00:18:12.592 --> 00:18:15.470 position:50% align:center
on my long journey
to the afterlife.

00:18:15.553 --> 00:18:20.558 position:50% align:center
I've made my peace with
where I am for now.

00:18:20.642 --> 00:18:23.478 position:50% align:center
I was born into privilege
as Kiyomori's daughter,

00:18:23.561 --> 00:18:28.233 position:50% align:center
became the emperor's wife,
bore His Majesty's child,

00:18:28.316 --> 00:18:31.528 position:50% align:center
enjoyed the endless beauty
of the passing seasons,

00:18:31.611 --> 00:18:35.281 position:50% align:center
never knowing the misery
of hunger nor cold.

00:18:35.365 --> 00:18:39.369 position:50% align:center
To find myself in such glory
and prosperity by fate's hand,

00:18:39.452 --> 00:18:43.039 position:50% align:center
it often felt as if I
were in heaven on earth.

00:18:46.584 --> 00:18:48.211 position:50% align:center
