together besieged in battle,

00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:56.553 position:50% align:center
surrounded by water
we could not drink.

00:18:56.636 --> 00:18:59.723 position:50% align:center
I was reminded that
all things must pass.

00:18:59.806 --> 00:19:02.308 position:50% align:center
Before my very eyes I
stood and witnessed...

00:19:02.392 --> 00:19:04.394 position:50% align:center
...the death of my child.

00:19:06.229 --> 00:19:08.398 position:50% align:center
I have endured all
forms of suffering.

00:19:08.481 --> 00:19:10.025 position:50% align:center
Through the pain I
have been granted

00:19:10.108 --> 00:19:14.279 position:50% align:center
a certain kind of wisdom.

00:19:14.362 --> 00:19:18.616 position:50% align:center
I understand so much more
than I could've ever imagined.

00:19:18.700 --> 00:19:22.620 position:50% align:center
Truly, all I wanted
was the Sacred Treasures,

00:19:22.704 --> 00:19:26.124 position:50% align:center
not the lives of
your whole clan.

00:19:26.207 --> 00:19:29.461 position:50% align:center
Your Majesty, they say
at the bottom of the sea

00:19:29.544 --> 00:19:31.963 position:50% align:center
sits the Dragon Palace Castle.

00:19:33.506 --> 00:19:37.510 position:50% align:center
Through the years, I've
often dreamt of its splendor.

00:19:37.594 --> 00:19:38.970 position:50% align:center
