the fabric of who I am.

00:20:12.295 --> 00:20:14.381 position:50% align:center
When those begin to come loose,

00:20:14.464 --> 00:20:17.717 position:50% align:center
I press my hands
together and pray.

00:20:17.801 --> 00:20:20.136 position:50% align:center
I think of the people I love,

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:24.599 position:50% align:center
and pray for their peace and
happiness in the next world.

00:20:24.683 --> 00:20:28.812 position:50% align:center
That small act is
all that I can do.

00:20:32.649 --> 00:20:34.818 position:50% align:center
[TOKUKO] The person who
shared that with me

00:20:34.901 --> 00:20:37.862 position:50% align:center
